Package com.mygdx.game.Core.Chef

Class MasterChef

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mygdx.game.Core.Scriptable
      • com.mygdx.game.Core.Chef.MasterChef
  • public class MasterChef
extends Scriptable
    This class manages the chefs and their inputs. Letting the player control them. This class is the players main access point into the game outside of UI elements. BlackCatStudio's Code and a few functions from team triple 10s
    Author:
    Felix Seanor, Jack Vickers, Jack Hinton, Sam Toner
